  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.56,
      608.95,
      575.05,
      684.55
    ],
    "text": "The low-pressure area located northeast of the Sri Lanka, still persist. This system is expected to move away from Sri Lanka during the next 36 hours. Under the influence of this system, wind speed and rainy conditions over the sea areas around the island may increase in the coming days.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.56,
      687.49,
      574.81,
      735.46
    ],
    "text": "The naval and fishing communities are requested to be attentive to the future forecasts and bulletins issued by the Department of Meteorology in this regard. Condition of Rain:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      3.0,
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.56,
      741.46,
      430.13,
      752.5
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the sea areas around the island.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.56,
      758.5,
      574.98,
      893.76
    ],
    "text": "Winds: Winds will be South-westerly. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to (50-60) kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Trincomalee to Pottuvil via Kankasanthurai, Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota. State of Sea: The sea areas off the coasts extending from Trincomalee to Pottuvil via Kankasanthurai, Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota will be rough at times. The other sea areas around the island can be moderate. The swell waves (about 2.0 \u2013 2.5 m) height (this is not for land area) may increase in the sea areas off the coast extending from Puttalam to Pottuvil via Colombo, Galle and Hambantota.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.56,
      896.33,
      490.88,
      917.16
    ],
    "text": "Temporarily strong gusty winds and very rough seas can be expected during thundershowers.",
